    Class Description
    BentWire
    Bent wire blocks are one of four kinds of wires, which transmit signals without affecting or being affected by them.
    BentWireActive
    Active bent wires are the active form of bent wires.

    Corner pipes are one of three basic kinds of pipes, which supply blocks and items to powered devices they are attached to.

    Detector switches activate whenever a mob is inside them.

    Pipes are devices that will draw items from components and deliver them to components that use them.

    Power sticks are special components that will supply power if and only if they are not powered themselves.
    PowerStickInactive
    Inactive power sticks are the active form of power sticks.
    PressSwitch
    Press switches are components that can be set to supply or not supply a current at the user's control.
    PressSwitchActive
    Active press switches are the active form of press switches.
    ProximityDetector
    Proximity detectors activate whenever mobs are near them.

    Wire
